; Coverage for op.cc
; Recursive print_cons exercises the O_CONS printing when there are
; multiple function arguments. With 4 arguments, print_cons recurses
; through nested O_CONS nodes to print "expr1, expr2, expr3, expr4".

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $100.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --format "%(justify(amount / 0, 20, -1, true))\n" -> 1
__ERROR__
While evaluating value expression:
  justify((amount / 0), 20, -1, true)
While calling function 'justify (<#EXPR (amount / {0})>, <#EXPR {20}>, <#EXPR {-1}>, 1)':
While handling posting from "$FILE", line 7:
>     Expenses:Food    $100.00
Error: Divide by zero
end test
